using graphics lib
	the-Window : the graphics panel

	Triangle : a triangle
	Triangle's Size : 100
	Triangle's Position : { 0, the std height ÷ 2}
	add Triangle to the-Window

	Rotation : every 2 ticks do
		change Triangle heading by 2 degrees

	Movement : every 1 tick do
		change Triangle x-pos by 4

	animate at 60 ticks per second
		animate Movement
		animate Rotation
		update the-Window
	… until
		(Triangle's x-Pos) ≥ the std width

"Finished" ↲
